# Outreach & email (EbookGamez / LearnForge)

## Partnership mail (SCORE, SBDC, nonprofits)

- **Never auto-send** partnership emails without explicit user approval.
- Default workflow: **create a Gmail draft** (via Gmail MCP), not send.
- Always **CC `ebookgames@yahoo.com`**.
- Optional Reply-To: `ebookgames@yahoo.com`.

## Signature block

```
Damond Morris
702-379-0396
ebookgames@yahoo.com
```

## Channel split

| Task | Tool |
|------|------|
| SCORE / SBDC / partner outreach | Gmail (draft → user sends) |
| Literary Club / subscriber welcome | Resend (`server/newsletter.ts`) |
| Replies & CC archive | Yahoo inbox |

