## EbookGamez vs LearnForge

- **EbookGamez**: admin password → `x-admin-token` → `/admin/outreach`
- **LearnForge**: Clerk owner email → `/owner/outreach`
- Share the same Resend audience ID for one subscriber list across both sites.

## Constraints

- No auto-send to SCORE/SBDC without approval.
- Resend free tier / Replit connector OK; avoid paid marketing SaaS lock-in.
